@BulkApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5000

### Health check
GET {{BulkApi_HostAddress}}/api/v1/ingest/health

### Manually enqueue a file
POST {{BulkApi_HostAddress}}/api/v1/ingest/file
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bucket": "bulk-ingest",
  "objectKey": "batch/2026/07/05/data.parquet"
}

### S3 ObjectCreated webhook
POST {{BulkApi_HostAddress}}/api/v1/ingest/s3-event
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Records": [
    {
      "eventName": "ObjectCreated:Put",
      "s3": {
        "bucket": { "name": "bulk-ingest" },
        "object": { "key": "batch/2026/07/05/part-00001.parquet", "size": 45000000 }
      }
    }
  ]
}
